node_5.subject: Abigail Chen
node_5.description: This is Abigail Chen's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 8:00 am, go to the hobb cafe at 9:00 am to cook and eat breakfast with other Love Ville participants, explore the Ville Village and engage in creative activities from 10:00 am to 12:00 pm, have lunch at a local restaurant at 12:30 pm, attend a digital art workshop from 2:00 pm to 4:00 pm, return to the hobb cafe at 6:00 pm to cook and eat dinner with other Love Ville participants, participate in a group social activity at the Ville Village from 7:00 pm to 9:00 pm, relax and reflect on the day from 9:00 pm to 11:00 pm.
